  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency support to Rohingya refugees affected by fire in refugee camps in Cox&#x2019;s Bazar</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this project is to provide life-saving shelter and basic household item assistance to Rohingya refugees. This UNHCR project provides 1) basic household items and shelter and 2) messages on available assistance/protection services to refugees. The project provides life-saving assistance to approximately 48,000 people, including 13,000 women, 11,000 men, 24,000 children, and 480 people with disabilities.</narrative>
  </description>
